This token is only for collectors.  

KEX collections,  is a limited series of artworks dedicated to Frogs of Phanes (Pepe-discs) collectors.

KEX are the represantation of the crypto-world's sufferings, inspired by ancient greek mythology and lore, crypto and pepe culture.

If you collect these tokens avoid listing/selling.You should consider keeping them "safe" in Pepe-Pandora's box (multisig) !!! For more info contact Phanes..(@alekxsys)

Some words:

Pluto (Ploutōn, Πλούτων), the ruler of the dead and the consort of Persephone, became conflated with Plutus (Ploutos, Πλοῦτος), wealth. 

Charon's obol is an allusive term for the coin placed in or on the mouth of a dead person before burial, it as a payment or bribe for Charon, the ferryman who conveyed souls across the river that divided the world of the living from the world of the dead.  KEΞ
